lyrics:
Started with hope, a tale untold,
In shadows concealed, love turned cold.
No time to weep, childhood's stolen sun,
A tragic love, dreams undone.

Amara, born into the dark,
Fatherless, motherless, a silent spark.
Stepfather, a hidden demon's mark,
Brother Tobias, poetry in the dark.

Mysterious dreams, reality entwined,
Amara's heart within darkness confined.
Revenge's shadow, always behind,
In the night's depths, a painful bind.

A scream lost in shadows deep,
Amara's heart in eternal sleep.
Dreams drowned reality, secrets keep,
The story ends, the pain still seeps.

[Verse]
In the shadows I stand, all alone
Lost in a world of darkness and unknown
A symphony of tears pouring from my soul
Drowning in emotions, I can't control

[Chorus]
Oh, the pain, it cuts me deep
Through the turbulence, my heart does weep
This dramatic melody, haunting and stark
Leads me deeper into the abyss, in the dark
